Pete,

You may find that in the long run it would be better to forgot the 
vent window. Get a solid piece from a the right side of a junk bus, 
buy a seal, and put it in the left side. Those little windows are 
usually the source of a lot of rust problems in buses. Should be a 
cheap fix.

